original_title: Parents Matter: Raising Kids with Integrity
overview: In a culture that throws it's hands up, tells parents they can't make a difference and belittles the parent's influence with "Patsy" commercials...We want you to know that YOU MATTER! You are your kids' PARENT, not their friend. The values you pass on and the faith you live, make a difference in the lives of your children, not just here, but for eternity.
title: Parents Matter: Raising Kids with Integrity
